title: [NDS]Bomberman_Land_Touch_2[www.the-data-base.co.uk]
description: Bomberman Land Touch! 2 is the follow up sequel to the smash-hit 2006 game on the Nintendo DS. Embark on a fun-filled, theme park adventure as you discover intrigue and a host of addicting mini-games that can be played by yourself or with up to 4 of your friends. And if the 40 mini-games weren&#039;t enough to fulfill your multiplayer action needs, the original Bomberman Battle game is included! Battle up to 8 friends via Nintendo Wireless Communications or go head to head via Nintendo Wi-Fi Connection. ESRB Rated E for Everyone
